ke":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e4a90991c75d76bba926d63b87d8895f2644666","tid":2504844,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"8e6eea836d8ff8ae416673407fcabf9d4f84dbab","tid":2504844,"uid":357710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45d8b81844d0363d2a28178ef6023a0f293989ac","tid":2504844,"uid":236140,"like":15,"dislike":11,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"唔知點解全私樓會係一個特別嘅賣點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當自己係南區/半山嗰班有錢人<br />\n<br />\n康城啲單位有一半都10,000,000樓下，全部咪又係基層出身 <br />\n<br />\n買餸食飯全部依靠連鎖店，買乜都貴過人，去街市買條魚都貴人幾十蚊 .... 咁樣叫優質生活？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大圍都唔係啲咩特別好區，不過衣食住行真係方便到不得了.... 大把小店，大排檔，打冷，串燒，街市啲嘢又平又靚<br />\n<br />\n14分鐘唔使轉車去到金鐘，班蝗蟲搭火車死返上去又方便... 邊有得輸<br />\n<br />\n利申：柏傲莊打手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"依家大圍去紅磡慢慢碌都要15分鐘，多二個站過埋海同我講14分鐘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfVKKSt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfVKKSt.png&h=fb6f933e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你啱，我記錯咗，銷售文件寫 17分鐘 <br />\n<br />\n吹大左，非常抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:21:56.000Z","msg":"九龍塘去紅磡唔知係咪多人投訴嘈音，開得蟻爬咁慢，成5分鐘一個站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大圍去九龍塘過隧道最少要5分鐘, 去會展站又站<br />\n過海，要幾耐無人知道。"},{"pid":"dce3e14ce34c906412ef669696503b0800ea4273","tid":2504844,"uid":22173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d21742614bd017ff336e62bfef3006fb06632e9","tid":2504844,"uid":236140,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:36:04.000Z","m